title: 4 French Learning Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 4 French Learning Books. The 2 PDFs are French editions & the 2 ePUBs are English editions:

1. Better Reading French - A Reader and Guide to Improving Your Understanding of Written French (ePUB)
2. Grammaire Progressive Du Francais - Debutant [French] (PDF)
3. The Ultimate French Review and Practice (2nd Ed) (ePUB)
4. Vocabulaire Progressif Du Francais avec 250 exercices (French) (PDF)
